reviewText:
Best Lando Buzanka movie ever, distant second "vedo nudo" if u can find it ,good luck.
very funny, intense , deep yet very light and amusing. wish it was colored.
reflects every man's dream, 3 testicles, even if born poor . all used for good cause and not violence.
relatively slow in today standards but still a milestone in movie making and must and should become a movie classic (with English translation of course)
